{"tid":1701033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女指揮官叫警曱唔好同街坊對罵 無人理佢","createTime":"2019-11-08T20:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T21:30:49.000Z","uid":25797,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7fac04253cd3e775b12b804fe60bf77ccb30cf","tid":1701033,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/739444856559186/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fvideos%2F739444856559186%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=d63c00e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/739444856559186/</a><br />\n<br />\n【將軍澳回顧】警員展高度服從性<br />\n<br />\n防暴警員於凌晨時分擅闖私人屋苑，期間與住戶不停對罵。有女指揮官大叫警員停止對罵，警員隨即展開高度服從性，在情緒激動時亦不忘服從上司指令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《警察(紀律)規例》<br />\n(第232章第45條).<br />\n違紀行為<br />\n(1)<br />\n任何督察或初級警務人員，如犯第(2)款所指明的違紀行為，並 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<br />\n在適當審裁體席前認罪；或<br />\n(b)<br />\n經適當審裁體裁斷犯罪，<br />\n則可由該審裁體按照本規例予以懲罰。<br />\n(2)<br />\n違紀行為指 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<br />\n沒有許可或妥善因由而擅離職守；<br />\n(b)<br />\n當值時睡覺；<br />\n(c)<br />\n對良好秩序及紀律有損的行為；<br />\n(d)<br />\n執行職責時怯懦；<br />\n(e)<br />\n違反警察規例或任何書面或口頭的警察命令；<br />\n(f)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不服從上級；</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(g)<br />\n由於昏醉而不適宜執行職責；<br />\n(h)<br />\n疏於職守或忽視命令；<br />\n(i)<br />\n裝病；<br />\n(j)<br />\n在執行職責的過程中，或在關乎警隊履行任何職責或職能方面，作出在要項上屬虛假的陳述；<br />\n(k)<br />\n不合法或不必要地行使權能，引致其他人或政府蒙受損失或損害；<br />\n(l)<br />\n蓄意破壞政府財產或因疏忽致令政府財產遺失或損壞；<br />\n(m)<br />\n其行為刻意致使公共服務聲譽受損。"},{"pid":"399f55603d644e2133b7d3defd550e14ae869fad","tid":1701033,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafaaffc652650cf66856b4d4f4daf2a95c02b36","tid":1701033,"uid":116054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:46:10.000Z","msg":"而家開槍都唔使寫報告，唔聽你指揮有鬼後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b983ee18e6ab891c54fee6183aa56fe39ae2ad3c","tid":1701033,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de523984484c9baa8eede6281fe33e4903b23e5","tid":1701033,"uid":111198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:47:33.000Z","msg":"最後都有停 狗仔真乖"},{"pid":"e7998f6d01a63000d42a3fed80b0365a002d9c91","tid":1701033,"uid":9315,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:47:36.000Z","msg":"我係個指揮官就會抆槍啡鳩隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔聽話呀嗱"},{"pid":"5fa0b534291b94cb0ed14360a46da9a9ea1d1004","tid":1701033,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aafaaffc652650cf66856b4d4f4daf2a95c02b36","tid":1701033,"uid":116054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:46:10.000Z","msg":"而家開槍都唔使寫報告，唔聽你指揮有鬼後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:48:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1701028/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1701028/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n可以連埋呢個post睇，白衫條狗鏈唔夠硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a6d1efe0cf3a99ef1e275668f51963eb83d46b","tid":1701033,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"192746abbc2a10aa4d4a5e5f9367b1dc602c3e91","tid":1701033,"uid":155224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:50:50.000Z","msg":"講真, 個個蒙面無林巴, 佢地自己都分唔到邊個打邊個啦, 洗咩聽白衫指揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c595001906933227745ee58785175266fa2d67d3","tid":1701033,